The Swell Season issue suicide tragedy statement to Hot Press
Glen and Marketa say they're "shocked and saddened."
The Swell Season have issued the following statement to Hot Press about the suicide last night of a man at their gig in the Saratoga Mountain Winery.
“The band, crew and all involved with them are shocked and saddened by the unfortunate events of last night. Their hearts go out to the victim and his friends and family.”